    "title": "Vacancy for Store Manager at Milton International Enterprises",
    "description": "Milton International Enterprises is actively seeking a talented and motivated Store Manager to join our dynamic team in Ghaziabad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Milton International Enterprises:\nMilton International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Learning & development budget\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Milton International Enterprises!",
